race.comment: MONTANA ICON (1) placed in a Grade 4/5 when a neck second this course and distance last time in a personal Best Time (28.51) and also clocked one of the quickest times on the card. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. LIZARD COUNTRY (7) was safely held last time out, finishing seventh at this track over 500m behind Joni Black (28.91) in a Restricted WIN H. Was in the money prior to that. Form from his last run is proving strong. Can measure up this time. HIGHLAND JACK (6) was below best at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth at Ballarat, but was among the placings at this track three back. Can feature with the right run. PENGUIN PAT (8) is in winning form and worth including in the main hopes.
